  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >72 Total HO scenes</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24 chapters</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Butterfly Album</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes a new minigame called Color by Pixel</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>Collector's Edition</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 extra locations</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 minigames</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wallpapers</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A music player</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New Friends</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take to the skies and fly with your newfound flock of feathered friends through challenging puzzles, beautiful locales, and more in I Love Finding Birds — a classic Hidden Object game that'll have your heart soaring!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161330/extras/d5c11b6dded818da7621ea0f66db55ac.poster.avif?t=1729509933\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161330/extras/d5c11b6dded818da7621ea0f66db55ac.webm?t=1729509933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161330/extras/d5c11b6dded818da7621ea0f66db55ac.mp4?t=1729509933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >My Birds</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet and befriend 20 different birds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161330/extras/2f20f41632112a4bb209e50e52082e3a.poster.avif?t=1729509933\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161330/extras/2f20f41632112a4bb209e50e52082e3a.webm?t=1729509933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161330/extras/2f20f41632112a4bb209e50e52082e3a.mp4?t=1729509933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Minigames</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Treat yourself to over 20 exciting and new minigames!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161330/extras/17ecfd9d723a53cd1e6a9ef7bb74e458.poster.avif?t=1729509933\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161330/extras/17ecfd9d723a53cd1e6a9ef7bb74e458.webm?t=1729509933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161330/extras/e9b6a4fcd0101c8bd4c1cefc3116add1.poster.avif?t=1729509933\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161330/extras/e9b6a4fcd0101c8bd4c1cefc3116add1.webm?t=1729509933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Meet the birds that helped our ideas take flight! Check out I Love Finding Birds!</strong></p>",
